    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《Rock Digger》，这是一个你扮演岩石角色的温馨采矿冒险！<br>探索程序生成的星球，挖掘矿物，用它们通过炼金术升级你的身体。发现失落的外星科技与力量。扔出亿万把镐？试着挖到足够深，直达星球核心。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挖掘</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不知为何拥有无限的镐。<br>扔向墙壁来挖掘。升级它们。蓄力扔出一个巨型镐。找到一个镐加特林？还有更多！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/5f8f4e2e382fa1a6c619d764975151b5.poster.avif?t=1749850990\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/5f8f4e2e382fa1a6c619d764975151b5.webm?t=1749850990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/5f8f4e2e382fa1a6c619d764975151b5.mp4?t=1749850990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级与科技</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你一无所有——甚至没有腿！也没有生命。但你将能够发现无数的新力量、外星科技，并将你的能力升级到不可思议的水平。从一块谦卑的岩石开始，进化为岩石之神！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/678e86a95db462cc7426d7c99da93523.poster.avif?t=1749850990\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/678e86a95db462cc7426d7c99da93523.webm?t=1749850990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/678e86a95db462cc7426d7c99da93523.mp4?t=1749850990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无计时器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Rock Digger》是一款专注于挖掘的游戏。你有的是时间。<br>地表没有什么在等着你，也不用防御怪物的攻击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解谜与小游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地下探索时，你经常会遇到谜题甚至小游戏！使用各种能力与它们互动，赢取奖励！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/a1e5bf8fc9a39ea8bd3e697ff6e9457f.poster.avif?t=1749850990\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/a1e5bf8fc9a39ea8bd3e697ff6e9457f.webm?t=1749850990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/a1e5bf8fc9a39ea8bd3e697ff6e9457f.mp4?t=1749850990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索外星世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你首次坠落的外星世界拥有众多生物群落和隐藏的秘密，等待你去发现，探索内容丰富。当你探索完毕后，还能发现全新世界，那里有更多的生物群落与秘密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/f114e2c5193207906e58ffbe1a819176.poster.avif?t=1749850990\" width=524 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/f114e2c5193207906e58ffbe1a819176.webm?t=1749850990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/f114e2c5193207906e58ffbe1a819176.mp4?t=1749850990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/aac673a8eca9bb288996a39872216f72.poster.avif?t=1749850990\" width=524 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/aac673a8eca9bb288996a39872216f72.webm?t=1749850990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/aac673a8eca9bb288996a39872216f72.mp4?t=1749850990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存于恶劣环境</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个游戏中，你不会遇到敌人。但你仍需谨慎，因为大自然本身也可能是致命的威胁。没有适当的准备就深入太深，黑暗会开始伤害你。一步踏错，你可能会掉进岩浆坑中。做好准备，保持警惕，活下来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/65b00afb51152cb8f096dac8887d2bdd.poster.avif?t=1749850990\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/65b00afb51152cb8f096dac8887d2bdd.webm?t=1749850990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3096260/extras/65b00afb51152cb8f096dac8887d2bdd.mp4?t=1749850990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
